      "raw_text": "COLFAX. Oct. 17.-All records for\ngate receipts at the county fair were\nbroken yesterday when $3.50 was TAX\nen- in. The weather has been splendid\nand the attractions in the way of char\nlot races and the regular track races\nhave been Of high order. The automo-\nbile race yesterday was failure, owing\nto a breakdown, but a two-mle exhi\nbition proved very interesting. Last\nnights dance at the armory was wei\npatronized."
    }
